item.title: CVE-2020-5004|2024-09-16T17:44:16.831Z -- ibm -- rational%20team%20concert
item.description: IBM Jazz Foundation products are vulnerable to cross-site scripting. This vulnerability allows users to embed arbitrary JavaScript code in the Web UI thus altering the intended functionality potentially leading to credentials disclosure within a trusted session. IBM X-Force ID: 192957.
